==English==
===Noun===
'''regular polygon''' (''Plural:'' '''regular polygons''')

#In [[geometry]], [[polygon]] which is both [[equiangular]] and [[equilateral]] (i.e. having all sides the same length and all interior angles the same).  Example: a [[square]] is a regular polygon, a non-square [[rectangle]] or a non-right [[parallelogram]] is not.